bug.short_desc: Pen input works incorrectly after update
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
Description of problem: Updating libinput causes the stylus to work incorrectly. Downgrading libinput fixes the problem.
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): 0.23.0-2.fc25
How reproducible: Install latest libinput. Attempt to draw.
Steps to Reproduce: 1. Install latest libinput. 2. Open up any drawing program (Xounal, GIMP, etc) 3. Attempt to draw.
Actual results: Drawing dots(tapping the screen in multiple places in a drawing program) will draw lines to the previous dots.
Expected results: Individual dots while drawing.
Additional info:
0.19.1-3.20160929.fc25 works as expected.
